1752. Check if Array Is Sorted and Rotated

Simply count the number of drops in the array. If there are more than 1 drops, then it is not sorted and rotated. If there is 0 or 1 drop, then it is sorted and rotated.


class Solution {
    public boolean check(int[] nums) {
        int n = nums.length;
        int dropCount = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (nums[i] > nums[(i + 1) % n]) {
                dropCount++;
            }
        }
        return dropCount <= 1;
    }
}